(ex gg being (Point of G) st (ex ff being (Point of F) st (ex v being (Element of ( REAL 2 )) st (((g = gg & f = ff) & v = <* ||. gg .||,||. ff .|| *>) & ( NORMGF . (g,f) ) = |. v .|)))) by A3;
